---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Shohei Toguchi | Unmuting Ryukyu">

	<!-- HERO -->
	<section style="padding:80px 32px 72px;background:#1C2C4F;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-bottom:4px solid #8B1D25;">
		<div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:5px;height:100%;background:#8B1D25;"></div>
		<div style="position:absolute;right:-40px;bottom:-20px;font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;font-size:200px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);line-height:1;user-select:none;pointer-events:none;">人</div>
		<div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1;">
			<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.3em;margin:0 0 16px 0;">About</p>
			<h1 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,64px);font-weight:700;color:#F0EBE3;margin:0 0 8px 0;line-height:1.05;">Shohei Toguchi</h1>
			<p style="font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:17px;color:#A8B8C8;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Documentary filmmaker. Sanshin performer. Cultural bridge between Okinawa and the world.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- STORY -->
	<section style="padding:80px 32px 96px;background:#F0EBE3;">
		<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">

			<div style="margin-bottom:64px;">
				<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:16px;margin-bottom:28px;">
					<div style="width:4px;height:24px;background:#8B1D25;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
					<div>
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.25em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">The Origin</p>
						<h2 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,30px);font-weight:700;color:#1C2C4F;margin:0;line-height:1.2;">Why I Started This</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p style="color:#4A3F3B;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.95;margin:0 0 20px 0;">
					When I studied in the UK, I realized something painful: the world knows Japan, but almost nobody knows Okinawa. Our language, our music, our history — they were invisible.
				</p>
				<p style="color:#4A3F3B;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.95;margin:0;border-left:3px solid #8B1D25;padding-left:20px;">
					That's when I decided to dedicate my work to one mission: <strong style="color:#1C2C4F;">bringing Okinawa's most precious things to the world through film.</strong>
				</p>
			</div>

			<div style="background:#1C2C4F;padding:48px;margin-bottom:64px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
				<div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:4px;height:100%;background:#8B1D25;"></div>
				<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.25em;margin:0 0 20px 0;">What I Believe</p>
				<h2 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,30px);font-weight:700;color:#F0EBE3;margin:0 0 20px 0;">Language is Peace</h2>
				<p style="color:#A8B8C8;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.95;margin:0;">
					Learning someone's language is the deepest form of respect. It's not just a skill — it's a peace movement. That's why I work across Japanese, English, Uchinaaguchi (Okinawan), and Mandarin Chinese to bridge cultures that have been separated for too long.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div style="margin-bottom:64px;">
				<div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:16px;margin-bottom:28px;">
					<div style="width:4px;height:24px;background:#8B1D25;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
					<div>
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.25em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Background</p>
						<h2 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,30px);font-weight:700;color:#1C2C4F;margin:0;line-height:1.2;">Skills & Experience</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:2px;background:#D0C5BA;">
					<div style="background:#fff;padding:28px;">
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 10px 0;">Languages</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Japanese, English (EIKEN 1 / TOEIC 955), Uchinaaguchi, Mandarin Chinese</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#F0EBE3;padding:28px;">
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 10px 0;">Filmmaking</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Premiere Pro, Documentary Production, AI-Enhanced Editing</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#fff;padding:28px;">
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 10px 0;">Culture</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Sanshin Performance, Eisa, Ryukyuan History & Oral History</p>
					</div>
					<div style="background:#F0EBE3;padding:28px;">
						<p style="color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 10px 0;">Community</p>
						<p style="color:#1C2C4F;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;">Global Shapers (WEF), Journal Okinawa Writer</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div style="background:#8B1D25;padding:48px;text-align:center;">
				<h3 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#F0EBE3;margin:0 0 16px 0;">Let's Work Together</h3>
				<p style="color:rgba(240,235,227,0.75);font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:15px;margin:0 0 32px 0;line-height:1.9;">Whether you need a documentary, social media content, or cultural consultation — I'd love to hear your story.</p>
				<div style="display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
					<a href="/contact/" style="text-decoration:none;background:#F0EBE3;color:#8B1D25;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:700;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.06em;">Contact Me</a>
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@letsgokinawa?sub_confirmation=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(240,235,227,0.4);color:#F0EBE3;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-weight:500;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.06em;">Watch on YouTube</a>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
